      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DAKOTA AVA (5) is a consistent dog overall, in the frame at 26 of 63 starts including 19 wins but missed the frame latest when fourth (26.10) over 455m at Murray Bridge. Form here sound including two wins. Happy to have her on top this line-up. ALGORITHM (7) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Hasty Holly (31.05) in a Grade 6. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Yet to score from this box but has never missed the frame in two starts. Bold showing expected. JUST A NUISANCE (1) turned in a solid run last start over 455m at Murray Bridge finishing 4th and beaten only 3.5 lengths (25.92). Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance.",
